nodes.text: Star Wars: Colouring Book (Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi)
Star Wars: Colouring Book is an activity book that was released as part of the Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi.

Revisit the Star Wars universe with the newest addition to the franchise, The Last Jedi. Join Rey, Finn and Poe to continue the adventure that started in The Force Awakens, and discover a host of new characters, ships and locations. Colour in scenes, characters and ships in this awesome movie colouring book.
